🧠 Dopamine Bro (Prefrontal Lab)

    "Master your dopamine. Reclaim your focus. Become the best version of yourself."

Dopamine Bro is your personal AI assistant for cognitive energy management. We’ve turned neuroscience into RPG mechanics, allowing you to see in real-time how your daily choices impact your brain's performance.
🚀 How It Works

We track your internal resources using two key metrics:

    Prefrontal Charge: Your reservoir of willpower, logic, and decision-making capacity. When this hits zero, focusing even on the simplest tasks becomes impossible.

    Limbic Heat: The activity level of your "inner beast." This rises from endless scrolling, sugar, and information noise. The higher the heat, the harder it is to say "no" to bad habits.

🔥 Key Features
1. Neural Garbage Collection (Sleep is the Base) 😴

In this app, sleep is your ultimate "magic pill."

    The Hard Reset: Only quality sleep fully clears your brain's cache.

    Morning Report: Get a briefing on how well your neurons "cleaned up" overnight. Find out if you're ready for deep work or if you should stay in power-saving mode.

2. Dynamic UI (Your Brain on Screen) 📊

Two interactive progress bars fluctuate based on your real-time actions:

    Working out? Charge +20%.

    Stuck in socials for an hour? Limbic Heat +40%.

    Walking without your phone? Heat -15%.

3. Bro-Notifications (The Honest Voice in Your Pocket) 🗣️

The app doesn't sugarcoat. It tells you the raw truth:

    "Bro, you've been staring at the screen for 30 minutes doing nothing. Your prefrontal cortex is fried. Go sleep or take a walk—you're just wasting time now."

4. Smart Time-Boxing ⏳

Automatic prompts suggesting when to take a break, meditate, or switch tasks based on your current "Charge" levels.
5. Limbic Firewall (Smart Time Tracker) 🛑

Control your digital habits before they control you.

    Custom Quota: Set a limit (e.g., 30 minutes). Once time is up, the app sends a high-priority alert.

    Real-time Damage: Notifications show exactly how much those 30 minutes drained your prefrontal percentage.

    Smart Reminders: The app reminds you of the high-value tasks on your list that you're currently trading for "cheap dopamine."

🧬 The Math of Your State

Our goal is to keep the ratio in favor of your reason, not your impulses. The algorithm calculates your current efficiency using the following formula:
Efficiency=LimbicHeatPrefrontalCharge​